msgctxt "1||fishing||text"
msgid "<color=batting_pitch_yellow>Color Commentator Miyaken's Advice</color>\r\n\r\nHow about <color=batting_pitch_yellow>scouting</color> to power up the team?\r\nCome to think of it, I think I saw a baseball player arguing\r\nwith a <color=batting_pitch_yellow>fisherman</color> down by the beach the other day!"
msgstr "<color=batting_pitch_yellow>Consiglio del telecronista Miyaken</color>\r\n\r\nChe ne dici di fare un po' di <color=batting_pitch_yellow>scouting</color> per rinforzare la squadra?\r\nOra che ci penso, l'altro giorno mi è parso di vedere un giocatore di baseball\r\ndiscutere con un <color=batting_pitch_yellow>pescatore</color> giù in spiaggia!"

msgctxt "2||snack||text"
msgid "<color=batting_pitch_yellow>Color Commentator Miyaken's Advice</color>\r\n\r\nPerhaps you need some <color=batting_pitch_yellow>new members</color>?\r\nI overheard some conversation about baseball at <color=batting_pitch_yellow>New Gaudi</color>, you know!"
msgstr "<color=batting_pitch_yellow>Consiglio del telecronista Miyaken</color>\r\n\r\nForse ti servono dei <color=batting_pitch_yellow>nuovi membri</color>?\r\nSai, ho sentito delle conversazioni sul baseball al <color=batting_pitch_yellow>New Gaudi</color>!"

msgctxt "3||ticket||text"
msgid "<color=batting_pitch_yellow>Color Commentator Miyaken's Advice</color>\r\n\r\nYour team is kinda hurting out there...\r\nWhy don't you use a <color=batting_pitch_yellow>Training Ticket</color> to whip those guys into shape?"
msgstr "<color=batting_pitch_yellow>Consiglio del telecronista Miyaken</color>\r\n\r\nLa tua squadra sta facendo un po' di fatica là fuori...\r\nPerché non usi un <color=batting_pitch_yellow>Biglietto addestramento</color> per rimettere quei ragazzi in forma?"

msgctxt "4||earned_runs||text"
msgid "<color=batting_pitch_yellow>Color Commentator Miyaken's Advice</color>\r\n\r\nYou're really giving up runs out there!\r\nYou've gotta <color=batting_pitch_yellow>switch out pitchers when their stamina runs out</color>."
msgstr "<color=batting_pitch_yellow>Consiglio del telecronista Miyaken</color>\r\n\r\nState subendo davvero troppi punti là fuori!\r\nDevi <color=batting_pitch_yellow>sostituire i lanciatori quando finiscono la resistenza</color>."

msgctxt "5||batting||text"
msgid "<color=batting_pitch_yellow>Color Commentator Miyaken's Advice</color>\r\n\r\nSeems like you're still kind of feeling your team out. Are you\r\nhaving trouble getting <color=batting_pitch_yellow>on base</color>? Your <color=batting_pitch_yellow>team's strength</color>\r\nwill go up if you get a hit during critical moments in the game."
msgstr "<color=batting_pitch_yellow>Consiglio del telecronista Miyaken</color>\r\n\r\nSembra che tu stia ancora cercando di inquadrare la tua squadra. Fai\r\nfatica ad arrivare <color=batting_pitch_yellow>in base</color>? La <color=batting_pitch_yellow>forza della tua squadra</color>\r\naumenterà se metti a segno una valida nei momenti critici della partita."

msgctxt "6||condition||text"
msgid "<color=batting_pitch_yellow>Color Commentator Miyaken's Advice</color>\r\n\r\nYour batters are going downhill here. Have you tried changing the lineup?\r\n Switching the lineup based on the player's <color=batting_pitch_yellow>condition</color> is one way to do it."
msgstr "<color=batting_pitch_yellow>Consiglio del telecronista Miyaken</color>\r\n\r\nI tuoi battitori stanno perdendo colpi. Hai provato a cambiare la formazione?\r\nModificarla in base alle <color=batting_pitch_yellow>condizioni</color> dei giocatori è un ottimo modo per farlo."
